# Title: File Download Via Bitsadmin To A Suspicious Target Folder
# Author: Florian Roth (Nextron Systems), Nasreddine Bencherchali (Nextron Systems)
# Date: 2022-06-28
# Level: high
# Description: Detects usage of bitsadmin downloading a file to a suspicious target folder
# MITRE Tactic: Defense Evasion
# Tags: attack.defense-evasion, attack.persistence, attack.t1197, attack.s0190, attack.t1036.003

CommandLine IN ("* /transfer *", "* /create *", "* /addfile *") CommandLine IN ("*:\\Perflogs*", "*:\\ProgramData\\*", "*:\\Temp\\*", "*:\\Users\\Public\\*", "*:\\Windows\\*", "*\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\*", "*\\AppData\\Roaming\\*", "*\\Desktop\\*", "*%ProgramData%*", "*%public%*") Image="*\\bitsadmin.exe" OR OriginalFileName="bitsadmin.exe"